Package net.minestom.server.tag

Class Tag<T>

java.lang.Object
net.minestom.server.tag.Tag<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the tag type
@NonExtendable public class Tag<T> extends Object
Represents a key to retrieve or change a value.

All tags are serializable.
